                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17931030-6-off27 t17931030-6-cd28"></join>, three linen sheets, value 8 s. a copper tea kettle, value 1 s. a linen counterpane, value 2 s. two check linen bed curtains, value 3 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17931030-6-victim90" type="victimName">
